Global Cable Harnesses Market Insights
Cable Harnesses Market size was valued at USD 20.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 34.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.4% from 2024 to 2030.

Cable Harnesses Market Overview
The global wire harness market is projected to reach USD 150.70 billion by 2030, up from USD 94.19 billion in 2023, reflecting a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 6.9% during the forecast period. This growth is driven by technological advancements in the automotive industry, increasing wire and cable consumption across various sectors, and the demand for lightweight wire harnesses to enhance fuel efficiency and reduce emissions. The Asia Pacific region dominated the market in 2022, with North America and Europe following as significant contributors.

